        {
            "title": "科威特因儲油設施滿載而削減石油產量",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0lsrebTgIkC2SqSg8KaJLQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB8N0NS_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據《華爾街日報》援引知情人士的報導,科威特在耗盡其原油儲存容量後,已開始減少部分油田的產量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示,該國正在討論將其生產和煉油產能限制在僅滿足國內消費所需的水平。預計未來幾天內將就這些更廣泛的減產措施做出決定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自與伊朗的衝突爆發以來,投資者一直對石油儲存問題感到擔憂,他們對《華爾街日報》的這一標題迅速做出反應,原油價格進一步上漲,美國股市則出現拋售。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">關閉油井可能對儲層壓力造成長期損害,並產生高昂的重啟成本,通常被視為最後手段。重啟生產可能需要數天甚至數週時間,具體取決於儲層情況。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-801b629d-f54a-397a-aaec-82038b2de7f8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著伊朗衝突導致海峽航運癱瘓,該地區主要石油生產國正在與時間賽跑。沙烏地阿拉伯和阿拉伯聯合大公國的主要儲存設施也在迅速填滿,預計兩國將在不到三週內達到其儲存極限。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一旦儲存設施滿載,生產商將面臨在技術和政治上都代價高昂的停產現實。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%91%E5%A8%81%E7%89%B9%E5%9B%A0%E5%84%B2%E6%B2%B9%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E6%BB%BF%E8%BC%89%E8%80%8C%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E7%94%A2%E9%87%8F-151052283.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-06 23:52:32",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
