        {
            "title": "聯儲會的戴利：必須繼續緊盯勞動力市場 雙重使命均面臨持續風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 舊金山聯儲行長瑪麗·戴利表示，令人失望的美國2月就業報告削弱了<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:勞動力;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/勞動力\">勞動力</a>市場正在企穩的看法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">戴利周五在接受CNBC採訪時說：「大家原本希望勞動力市場正在趨於穩定，或許這種希望有點過頭了，我們確實必須繼續緊盯勞動力市場。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，她強調，決策者不應對任何一個月的數據過於看重，並指出報告中的細節使其難以解讀。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國非農就業人數意外驟減 勞動力市場出現拐點的想法被徹底粉碎 (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">戴利表示，聯儲會雙重使命的兩方面都繼續面臨風險。她指出，通膨高於2%的目標已有五年。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-69d04f10-5b8c-379a-89f5-49f1d220d28d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我擔心的是，勞動力市場可能比我們迄今看到的要弱一些，但從去年夏天起我就一直在擔心這一點，」戴利說。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Daly Says Labor Market Weakness Shows Dual Risks Persist</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%9A%84%E6%88%B4%E5%88%A9-%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E7%B7%8A%E7%9B%AF%E5%8B%9E%E5%8B%95%E5%8A%9B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E9%9B%99%E9%87%8D%E4%BD%BF%E5%91%BD%E5%9D%87%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-144013958.html",
